<TIMEX3 tid="t3" type="DATE" value="2011-08-02">2 August 2011</TIMEX3> Last updated at 05:18 GMT Help Syrian forces are pushing towards the center of the city of Hama as they continue an offensive in which scores of people have died .
Residents told the BBC many people were fleeing to nearby villages , believing the army would gain full control .
On <TIMEX3 tid="t6" type="DATE" value="2011-08-01">Monday</TIMEX3> , security forces cracked down on protests in towns around Syria , often after prayers on the first day of the Muslim holy month of Ramadan .
The UN Security Council has resumed discussions on the crisis .
